These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, billiard, whist, snooker
House: palace, cape-cod, gothic-revival, ranch-style
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, almond-milk, lemonade, juice
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, thai, australian, turkish
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, azalea, marigold, balloon-flower
 1. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 2. the person drinking juice is between the person playing scrabble and the person who growsballoon-flower##2
 3. the polish is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 4. the thai is on the left of the australian##1
 5. the person who growssunflower is between the person playing scrabble and the person drinking lemonade##2
 6. the turkish is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
 7. the person who growsazalea is the person playing whist##1
 8. the person playing snooker is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 9. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
10. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |         3          |     4     |
| Game           | whist | scrabble   | snooker | billiard |
| House   | palace      | cape-cod | gothic-revival              | ranch-style |
| Beverage   | cola       | almond-milk     | juice               | lemonade    |
| Nationality           | thai        | australian     | turkish           | polish       |
| Flower     | azalea | marigold     | sunflower                | balloon-flower      |

