4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, davidoff, alhambra, oliveros
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, cooking, gardening, filmmaking
 1. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the canadian##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the egyptian##1
 3. the person watching mystery movies is between the indonesian and the davidoff-smoker##2
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 5. the alhambra-smoker is the person watching mystery movies##1
 6. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 7. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 8. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
 9. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
10. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
11. the person who's hobby is collecting is the indonesian##1
12. the egyptian is the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Nationality          | indonesian       | canadian      | egyptian      | italian      |
| Movie-Genre           | documentary | mystery | thriller | zombie |
