There 4 different types of food: eggplant, zucchini, spinach, scrabbleing
4 different games are played: whist, scrabble, canasta, mah-jongg
 1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person eating scrabbleing##1
 2. the person eating zucchini is between the person who growssunflower and the person playing canasta##2
 3. the person who growstulip is between the chinese and the egyptian##2
 4. the person playing whist is the owner of the dog##1
 5. the person eating spinach is the owner of the goldfish##1
 6. the person who growstulip is the indonesian##1
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is the chinese##1
 8. the indonesian is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 9. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
10. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person eating scrabbleing##1
11. the person eating scrabbleing is between the owner of the goldfish and the person playing mah-jongg##2
12. the person eating zucchini is between the person playing whist and the indonesian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |    3     |     4      |
| Nationality      | egyptian      | indonesian         | chinese | dutch      |
| Pet           | goldfish | horse | mouse | dog     |
| Flower   | bellflower         | tulip          | amaryllis  | sunflower |
| Food         | spinach        | scrabbleing  | zucchini | eggplant   |
| Game     | scrabble    | canasta         | mah-jongg     | whist     |

