.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-18::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, designer, project-manager, engineer
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, sunflower, amaryllis, poppy
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, 7up, fanta
4 different games are played: poker, domino, chess, monopoly
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, chestnut, azure, aquamarine
 1. the person drinking fanta is between the person playing chess and the person who likes chestnut##2
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
 3. the person playing domino is the person who likes azure##1
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1
 5. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the person playing domino is on the right of the designer##1
 7. the librarian is the person who growspoppy##1
 8. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 9. the engineer is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
10. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
11. the engineer is between the person who growspoppy and the person playing poker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |   4    |
| Job          | librarian  | engineer  | designer  | project-manager   |
| Flower   | poppy     | zinnia | amaryllis     | sunflower |
| Beverage           | 7up   | fanta     | iced-tea      | almond-milk   |
| Game         | chess   | monopoly    | poker  | domino |
| Color     | lavender | aquamarine     | chestnut | azure |

