.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-19::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, asparagus, apple, cucumber
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, handball, badminton, soccer
House: modern, townhouse, cape-cod, wooden
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, white, blue, aquamarine
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, pall-mall, tiparillo, montecristo
 1. the cape-cod house is the person who's sport is handball##1
 2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 3. the person eating asparagus is between the person who likes aquamarine and the wooden house##2
 4. the wooden house is the person who likes red##1
 5. the person eating kiwi is between the person eating asparagus and the montecristo-smoker##2
 6. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 7. the person who likes blue is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the tiparillo-smoker##1
 9. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the modern house##1
10. the person eating apple is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |       4       |
| Food      | cucumber    | asparagus     | kiwi        | apple          |
| Sport         | soccer | handball   | snowboarding        | badminton |
| House           | modern   | cape-cod | wooden | townhouse      |
| Color   | aquamarine    | white      | red          | blue        |
| Cigar     | old-henry  | pall-mall   | tiparillo      | montecristo           |

