.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, software-developer, firefighter, doctor
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, orchid, aconite, amaryllis
4 different pets are kept: snake, goat, pony, goldfish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, musical, disaster, romance
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, fonseca, dunhill, ritmeester
 1. the person who growsamaryllis is the owner of the goat##1
 2. the ritmeester-smoker is between the owner of the goldfish and the person watching family movies##2
 3. the fonseca-smoker is between the person watching musical movies and the dunhill-smoker##2
 4. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 5. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 6. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the doctor##1
 7. the software-developer is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 8. the person who growsaconite is the person watching disaster movies##1
 9. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
10. the teacher is the owner of the snake##1
11. the owner of the snake is the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Job         | firefighter  | software-developer | doctor | teacher |
| Flower   | amaryllis      | orchid   | aconite      | rose    |
| Pet   | goat  | pony | goldfish        | snake     |
| Movie-Genre         | family  | musical  | disaster     | romance      |
| Cigar     | chaman | ritmeester      | fonseca   | dunhill       |

 